Control Plane (can have multiple master nodes control planes for redudancy)
  1.API Server (entry point to K8s - UI, API, CLI)
  2. Controller Manager (Keeps track of whats happening to the cluster)
  3. Scheduler (ensures pods placement)
  4. etcd (holds the current state of the K8s state - backing store)

